---
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20 bg-background-subtle overflow-hidden">
  <div class="px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 max-w-[1440px] mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-text-main mb-6">
        Tres pasos. Dos minutos. Listo.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Sin tutoriales, sin configuraciones. Así de fácil.
      </p>
    </div>

    <ol class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-12 relative list-none p-0 m-0">
      <!-- Connection Line (Desktop) -->
      <div class="hidden md:block absolute top-1/2 left-0 w-full h-px bg-secondary-200 -z-10" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <li class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black text-primary-500 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-primary-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 mb-8 border border-secondary-100" aria-hidden="true">
          1
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-text-main mb-4">Registrate</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Solo tu email. Sin tarjeta, sin datos raros, sin esperas.
        </p>
      </li>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <li class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black text-primary-500 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-primary-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 mb-8 border border-secondary-100" aria-hidden="true">
          2
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-text-main mb-4">Subí tus productos</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Uno por uno o miles desde un Excel. El sistema te guía en cada paso.
        </p>
      </li>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <li class="flex flex-col items-center text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-black text-primary-500 shadow-xl group-hover:bg-primary-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 mb-8 border border-secondary-100" aria-hidden="true">
          3
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold text-text-main mb-4">Compartí y vendé</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          Pegá el link en tu bio, mandalo por WhatsApp o usalo como tu sitio web. Ya estás vendiendo.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <div class="mt-20 text-center">
      <a 
        href="https://admin.purocatalogo.com/register" 
        class="btn-primary h-12 px-10"
      >
        Creá tu catálogo gratis <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" aria-hidden="true">arrow_forward</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
